These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
City: prague, liverpool, nizza, colone
1. City:liverpool is on the left of City:prague##1
2. Food:mango == City:colone##1
3. City:nizza is on the right of City:prague##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of City:colone##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of City:prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| City   | liverpool  | prague     | nizza   | colone |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
House: palace, townhouse, futuristic, farmhouse
Sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. House:farmhouse == Sport:soccer##1
2. House:palace is on the far right##1
3. House:townhouse is on the right of House:farmhouse##1
4. House:farmhouse is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| House   | futuristic | farmhouse | townhouse | palace    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

