1. Pet:rabbit is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1
2. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Nationality:nigerian == Pet:pony##1
5. Pet:rabbit is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Pet     | frog  | rabbit    | guinea-pig       | pony |

 